Imagine what that would've done to your mama.

881
00:38:00,727 --> 00:38:04,496
我一辈子都在让她失望
I've disappointed her every day of my life.

882
00:38:04,498 --> 00:38:07,164
我唯一想要的就是她对我的尊重
And all I ever wanted was her respect.

883
00:38:07,166 --> 00:38:10,701
本以为如果我挽救了她宝贵的公司 我会获得尊重
Thought if I saved her precious company, I-I'd finally get it.

884
00:38:10,703 --> 00:38:12,536
我向你保证一件事情
Well, I'll promise you one thing,

885
00:38:12,538 --> 00:38:15,506
Angola的监狱顾问会给你足够多的时间
you'll have plenty of time to work through those mommy issues

886
00:38:15,508 --> 00:38:18,141
解决你的恋母情结
with the prison counselor at Angola.

887
00:38:22,380 --> 00:38:23,879
我会给国土安全部打电话
I'll call DHS,

888
00:38:23,881 --> 00:38:25,548
让他们来接他去审讯
have them pick him up for processing.

889
00:38:25,550 --> 00:38:27,283
Gregorio
Gregorio.

890
00:38:27,285 --> 00:38:28,718
你干得非常棒
You did good in there.

891
00:38:28,720 --> 00:38:30,186
谢谢
Thanks.

892
00:38:30,188 --> 00:38:31,821
你也不赖
You weren't so bad yourself.

893
00:38:32,857 --> 00:38:35,658
Roy 给我们一些时间好吗
Roy, will... you give us a minute?

894
00:38:37,061 --> 00:38:38,494
嘿 Lasalle
Hey, look, Lasalle,

895
00:38:38,496 --> 00:38:41,029
我知道我们一直合不太来 但今天是
I know we've been butting heads but today was like...

896
00:38:41,031 --> 00:38:42,497
巨大的成功
A huge success.

897
00:38:43,667 --> 00:38:45,133
都过去了
It was.

898
00:38:45,135 --> 00:38:46,802
毕竟 我们最终抓到了坏人
I mean, after all, we took down the bad guys,

899
00:38:46,804 --> 00:38:48,169
一天下来
and at the end of the day,

900
00:38:48,171 --> 00:38:49,871
这才是最重要的事情 对吗
that's all that really matters, right?

901
00:38:49,873 --> 00:38:52,708
是的 但我们还是因意见不合而大吵特吵
Right, but still, we were at each other's throats.

902
00:38:52,710 --> 00:38:55,410
这是成长的烦恼 自古都是如此
It's growing pains, ancient history.

903
00:38:55,412 --> 00:38:57,511
历史总是不断的重复
History tends to repeat itself.

904
00:38:57,513 --> 00:38:59,313
就我看来
As far as I'm concerned,

905
00:38:59,315 --> 00:39:01,281
因为我们都在乎 所以才吵架
we were arguing 'cause we both cared,

906
00:39:01,283 --> 00:39:03,584
这是件好事情
and that's a good thing.

907
00:39:03,586 --> 00:39:05,753
好吧 我同意
All right, I'm down with that.

908
00:39:05,755 --> 00:39:07,788
但 还是发生了
Still, it happened.

909
00:39:07,790 --> 00:39:11,459
所以 我们应该告诉Pride这血淋淋的细节 还是怎样
So, you think we can spare Pride the gory details, or what?

910
00:39:11,461 --> 00:39:14,461
这只是办公室的日常
It's just another day at the office down here.

911
00:39:14,463 --> 00:39:15,762
底线是
Bottom line,

912
00:39:15,764 --> 00:39:18,631
他不需要知道今天发生的所有事情
is he doesn't need to know anything about today.

913
00:39:21,102 --> 00:39:24,404
-哈喽 有人在家吗 -嘿
- Hello? Anybody home? - Hey!

914
00:39:24,406 --> 00:39:25,872
-嘿 -他来了
- Hey, man! - There he is!

915
00:39:25,874 --> 00:39:27,741
真高兴看你完好无缺的回来了
Hey, good to see you in one piece.

916
00:39:27,743 --> 00:39:28,975
你是完好无缺的吧
You are in one piece?

917
00:39:28,977 --> 00:39:31,042
当然 就一些小伤口
Oh, yeah, it's just a flesh wound.

918
00:39:31,044 --> 00:39:33,945
如果不是你们的话 会糟糕很多
Could've been a lot worse if it hadn't been for you all.

919
00:39:33,947 --> 00:39:35,283
我不在 你们干的不错
You did a good job without me.

920
00:39:35,307 --> 00:39:37,083
哦 是的
Oh, yeah.

921
00:39:37,084 --> 00:39:39,785
完全没有问题 就像上了油
This was seamless. It was like a well-oiled

922
00:39:39,787 --> 00:39:41,953
但又很吵的机器
but extremely loud machine.

923
00:39:41,955 --> 00:39:43,555
我需要知道这话什么意思吗
Do I want to know what that means?

924
00:39:43,557 --> 00:39:45,624
意思是 我们很高兴看到你回来
It means we're glad to have you back,

925
00:39:45,626 --> 00:39:47,658
主持大局
calling the shots.

926
00:39:47,660 --> 00:39:50,194
好的 那这样
Okay. In that case,

927
00:39:50,196 --> 00:39:52,797
我们先把文书工作放一边 去喝一杯吧
I say we forget the paperwork, go get a drink.

928
00:39:52,799 --> 00:39:53,308
哦
Oh!

929
00:39:53,332 --> 00:39:54,767
棒 正合我意
Yes. Now you're talkin' my language.

930
00:39:54,768 --> 00:39:55,554
第一轮我买单
First round's on me.

931
00:39:55,578 --> 00:39:57,068
恐怕我不能让你这么做
I'm afraid I can't let you do that.

932
00:39:57,069 --> 00:39:58,483
这是我作为绅士的责任
It's my gentlemanly responsibility.

933
00:39:58,507 --> 00:40:00,238
你这么说话真是
Literally makes me nauseous

934
00:40:00,239 --> 00:40:01,194
令我恶心
when you talk like that.

935
00:40:01,218 --> 00:40:02,908
他们一直这样吗
They been like this the whole time?

936
00:40:02,909 --> 00:40:04,341
-别提了 -别提了
- You have no idea. - You have no idea.

